rating_comment: One of the best Air BNB in Dhaka. The place was better than described or Advertised. Great Host!! Equipped with all Amenities. Very nice Kitchen. WIll stay again. Absolutely hassle-free living in Dhaka at this place. Next to Banani 11 where everything is available, shops, restaurants, bar you name it.
Decent stay for corporates staying over in Dhaka for a short time. Some basic amenities can be better
